<item>
            <title>[OPENJPA-1643] Use container-managed data sources as Slice</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OPENJPA-1643</link>
                <project id="12310351" key="OPENJPA">OpenJPA</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Slice currently only allows URL based configuration. In managed environment, Slice should allow configuration via a JNDI-named data source. For example, the following configuration&lt;br/&gt;
should be possible. The basic conditions are&lt;br/&gt;
  a) Specify the master slice as &amp;lt;jta-data-source&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  b) Specify each slice datasource (including the master) with openjpa.ConnectionFactoryName&lt;br/&gt;
  c) Specify usual &apos;managed&apos; modes if the slices participate in a JTA transaction&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The example below shows three slices named &apos;slice1&apos;, &apos;slice2&apos; and &apos;slice3&apos; connected to three configured data sources.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;        &amp;lt;persistence-unit name=&quot;Slice&quot; transaction-type=&quot;JTA&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    	    &amp;lt;provider&amp;gt;org.apache.openjpa.persistence.PersistenceProviderImpl&amp;lt;/provider&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    	    &amp;lt;jta-data-source&amp;gt;jdbc/slice-ds1&amp;lt;/jta-data-source&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;           &amp;lt;properties&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;property name=&quot;openjpa.BrokerFactory&quot; value=&quot;slice&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;property name=&quot;openjpa.slice.Names&quot; value=&quot;slice1,slice2,slice3&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;property name=&quot;openjpa.slice.Master&quot; value=&quot;slice1&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;property name=&quot;openjpa.slice.slice1.ConnectionFactoryName&quot; value=&quot;jdbc/slice-ds1&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;property name=&quot;openjpa.slice.slice2.ConnectionFactoryName&quot; value=&quot;jdbc/slice-ds2&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;property name=&quot;openjpa.slice.slice3.ConnectionFactoryName&quot; value=&quot;jdbc/slice-ds3&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;property name=&quot;openjpa.TransactionMode&quot; value=&quot;managed&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
               &amp;lt;property name=&quot;openjpa.ConnectionFactoryMode&quot; value=&quot;managed&quot; /&amp;gt; &lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/properties&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/persistence-unit&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
